<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/globals.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="about-main-container">
      <div class="about-left">
        <div class="about-card-imgs">
          <img
            src="/assets/card-img.png"
            alt="UPM Card"
            class="about-card-img card-1"
          />
        </div>
        <button class="about-register-btn">Register</button>
      </div>
      <div class="about-right">
        <h1 class="about-title">About PING ID</h1>
        <p class="about-desc">
          Secure, all-in-one identification card for every citizen of UPM.
        </p>
        <p class="about-body">
          The internet is still seen as a place of scams, delays, and wasted
          time, while government services remain trapped in dusty files and
          endless queues. Citizens struggle with slow, outdated processes,
          lacking transparency and quick access to essential services.
        </p>
        <h2 class="about-instructions-title">Login Instructions</h2>
        <div class="about-instructions">
          <p>Enter your registered name.</p>
          <ol>
            <li>Type in your numerical Ping Id and Password carefully.</li>
            <li>
              Once all information is entered, please review for accuracy.
            </li>
            <li>Click on the Submit button to complete the process.</li>
            <li>Wait for application to be processed.</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
